  <brief_title>A Comparison of Three Methods of Hemoglobin Monitoring in Pediatric Patients Undergoing Major Surgery</brief_title>
  <acronym>Hemoped</acronym>
  <official_title>Hemoglobin Monitoring During High Bleeding Risk Surgery in Pediatric Patients: Equivalence Study of Hemoglobin Transcutaneous Saturation and Hemocue With Total Serum Hemoglobin</official_title>
  <sponsors>
